NASA Astrophysics at this\ntime. The first exobiosphere discovery is likely to be such a major event that\nscientific and public pressure will produce new funding across a range of\ndisciplines, not just astrophysics, to study the nature of Life in the\nUniverse. Then will be the time when a broader science community can advocate\nfor a mission that will make definitive exobiosphere measurements.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 25 Sep 2015 17:30:37 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-09-28"}
